data.description: NEW LOW PRICE $355,000  LOOK UP ADORABLE IN THE DICTIONARY AND THIS HOME POPS UP Located on aprox.1/3 Acre. This up-dated 4 bedroom, 3 bath home has Hardwood Floors on both levels. Eat-in Kitchen has Corian counter tops, Smooth cooktop, Double Ovens & Built in Desk. Fridge to. This home is complete and ready for you to move right into. Lo remain. Large Pantry!  Laundry Rm with wash sink, Formal Living Rm, Dining Rm & Large Family Rm w/ Gas Log FP & Powder room. Up are 4 BRs(all with HW floors & good closets), 2 Remodeled Baths. Off Kitchen is a Large Deck overlooking fenced-in, landscaped yard. Play ground / kids fort & Shed to remain. Roof aprox.2017.  Call today for your personal showing!
